<h2>Projects</h2>

<h3>Inception <i>(2026)</i></h3>
<div>
A containerised infrastructure stack built with Docker Compose, featuring
Nginx (TLS 1.3), WordPress, MariaDB, Redis, an FTP server, a static site, and much more — all on
Alpine Linux with Docker Secrets for credential management.
</div>

<h3>Minishell <i>(2025)</i></h3>
<div>
A POSIX-compliant shell written in C, supporting pipes, redirections,
environment variables, and built-in commands. with semi-garbage-collector!
</div>

<h3>Philosophers <i>(2025)</i>
<div>
A solution to the dining philosophers problem using POSIX threads and
mutexes, exploring concurrent programming in C.
</div>
